Sessions
---------
Sessions are built using client-sessions. In order to revoke all sessions from server side, a token is used in accordance to this blog post:

https://hacks.mozilla.org/2012/12/using-secure-client-side-sessions-to-build-simple-and-scalable-node-js-applications-a-node-js-holiday-season-part-3/

Bugs
----
When installing Monk,
change: node_modules/monk/node_modules/mongodb/node_modules/bson/ext/index.js row 15 to bson = require('../browser_build/bson');
